### Notes

*   This article uses the [classical treatment of tensors](/Classical_treatment_of_tensors) and [Einstein summation convention](/Einstein_summation_convention), with a [Minkowski metric](/Minkowski_metric) of (+1, −1, −1, −1). When equations are specified for vacuum, they can also be seen as formulations in terms of total charge and current.
